---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Secure Workflows | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Secure AI-enabled workflows designed around governance, access control, review, and operational assurance."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Secure Workflows
      </p>

      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        AI workflows designed for control, governance, and trust.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI helps organisations integrate AI into operational processes while maintaining appropriate controls over information, review, approvals, and decision-making.
      </p>

      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The challenge
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI adoption requires more than model access.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Many organisations can access AI tools, but few have structured workflows that ensure information is handled appropriately, outputs are reviewed, and responsibilities remain clear.
          </p>

          <p>
            Without governance, AI can introduce operational, regulatory, reputational, and quality risks. Secure workflows provide the framework needed to use AI effectively while maintaining organisational controls.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          Core capabilities
        </p>

        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Governance built into the workflow.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Access control
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Restrict access to information, models, and workflows according to organisational roles and responsibilities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Review points
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Embed human review and approval steps before outputs are used operationally or externally.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Information security
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Ensure sensitive information remains within approved systems and controlled environments.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
              Workflow governance
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Define responsibilities, escalation paths, quality controls, and decision checkpoints.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Example applications
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Designed for operational environments where accountability matters.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI-assisted policy and regulatory advice requiring review and sign-off.
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Technical advisory workflows involving sensitive infrastructure and operational information.
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Internal knowledge systems that operate within approved organisational boundaries.
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI-enabled reporting, drafting, and evidence synthesis with embedded quality assurance.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>

          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Security and productivity should work together.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI combines AI deployment, governance, evidence management, and operational design into practical workflows that organisations can trust.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our approach focuses on enabling AI adoption while preserving accountability, quality, information security, and professional judgement.
          </p>

          <p>
            The result is AI that fits within existing organisational responsibilities rather than operating outside them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Deploy AI within workflows you can trust.
        </h2>

        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about secure AI workflows, governance frameworks, review processes, and controlled operational deployment.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
        >
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
